          "reviewBody": "JSPM's Cygnet Public School is one of the good schools having large campus with big ground. I think Ground is the must have thing for growing kids in their curriculum.\n\nAlthough, This campus have colleges under JSPM so once you admitted your pupil you can expect him graduated from same campus 😅\n\nStaff is nice and friendly as well as strict for which is much required.\n\nI'll share photos soon.",
